For more xmpp libraries or clients:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/170503/commandline-jabber-client

A good example:
https://github.com/fabianp/xmpp-shell.git

Ruby:
apt-get install rubygems
gem install session
gem install xmpp4r-simple

Perl:
apt-get install libnet-xmpp-perl

Python:
apt-get install python-xmpp
